title: >>> Moving FORWARD
body_text: Like every event prior, DODGEBALL 15 is another extravaganza that is looking to make history. DODGEBALL 15 could certainly do that seeing how the holiday has brought many friends back to their homes. This could be the main factor in a record-setting crowd tomorrow night. Many still remember the huge DODGEBALL XTWO and its 42 players. 15 could very well beat that record as new contenders are already scheduled to play. Whatever happens, you can bet that DODGEBALL 15 will be memorable event, as this incredible journey continues. The final November event of the year is coming, and coming fast ...
